Project:
Akka-Spring-Jetty-Websockets

Short description:
Spring Application that uses actor and web sockets for building
a push system in scope of sending data to web clients

Main technologies used:
    -Spring 3.2.2.REALEASE (no *.xml)
    -Akka actor 2.0 (for a messaging system)
    -Jetty Websockets 8.1.8.v20121106(for push data)
    -Servlet 3.0 (no web.xml)
    -Jetty container

Run the project:
    cd web/
    mvn jetty:run (within web/pom.xml)

Access the application:
    http://localhost:8080/Akka-Spring/index.jsp
